00:31:02,160 --> 00:31:04,400
I've just married into the family,
and you already can't stand me?

520
00:31:05,120 --> 00:31:07,400
Don't you know distance
makes the heart grow fonder?

521
00:31:07,480 --> 00:31:10,120
You'd get tired of the flowers
if you stayed with it every single day.

522
00:31:10,200 --> 00:31:12,360
Of course, you're prettier than flowers.

523
00:31:12,440 --> 00:31:14,320
Alright, now hurry up and go.

524
00:31:19,480 --> 00:31:20,320
Hello.

525
00:31:20,400 --> 00:31:23,120
<i>Something's happened at Hailan Port.</i>
<i>Get to the company now, Jinyu.</i>

526
00:31:23,200 --> 00:31:24,080
<i>Hurry!</i>

527
00:31:24,160 --> 00:31:26,280
<i>Listen, the place</i>
<i>is full of people demanding money.</i>

528
00:31:28,040 --> 00:31:28,960
<i>Come quickly!</i>

529
00:31:30,520 --> 00:31:32,800
Something came up at the company.
We have to go.

530
00:31:33,960 --> 00:31:34,920
Granny, we're heading out.

531
00:31:35,440 --> 00:31:37,280
- Maimai, I left the meal over there.
- Okay.

532
00:31:37,360 --> 00:31:38,680
- Heading out.
- Bye.

533
00:31:39,600 --> 00:31:40,440
Eat first.

534
00:31:42,120 --> 00:31:43,160
I'll keep playing.

535
00:31:45,200 --> 00:31:47,560
- Give us an explanation!
- You're an unethical business!

536
00:31:47,640 --> 00:31:49,400
- Hurry up!
- Give me an explanation!

537
00:31:49,480 --> 00:31:52,520
Everyone, please stop arguing. We've
already reported this to the company.

538
00:31:52,600 --> 00:31:54,360
Please stay calm and stop the noise, okay?

539
00:31:54,440 --> 00:31:56,240
- Stop the noise!
- Everyone, listen to me.

540
00:31:56,320 --> 00:31:58,160
Hailan Port has had issues before.

541
00:31:58,240 --> 00:31:59,800
They've been involved
in fraudulent fundraising.

542
00:31:59,880 --> 00:32:02,440
And now there's this matter
of swapping materials.

543
00:32:02,520 --> 00:32:04,320
Today, they must give us an explanation.

544
00:32:04,400 --> 00:32:05,280
- Right!
- Right!

545
00:32:05,360 --> 00:32:08,600
- Give us an explanation!
- We must get an answer today!

546
00:32:08,680 --> 00:32:12,280
It seems to me that all your projects
were obtained through illegal methods,

547
00:32:12,360 --> 00:32:14,760
specifically designed
to cheat us ordinary people.

548
00:32:14,840 --> 00:32:16,240
Today, if you don't give us
a proper explanation,

549
00:32:16,320 --> 00:32:17,720
you're not allowed to start work.

550
00:32:17,800 --> 00:32:20,640
- Right, no starting work!
- Everyone, please calm down first!

551
00:32:22,000 --> 00:32:22,880
Calm down!

552
00:32:22,960 --> 00:32:24,560
- Kai, what's going on?
- What happened?

553
00:32:24,640 --> 00:32:27,200
A wall collapsed at the construction site
this morning and broke a worker's leg.

554
00:32:27,280 --> 00:32:29,840
Then someone dug up
the old Hailan Port scandal again.

555
00:32:29,920 --> 00:32:31,960
Everyone's furious
and demanding an explanation.

556
00:32:33,120 --> 00:32:35,280
They're here! The boss is here!

557
00:32:36,720 --> 00:32:39,680
Don't move! Everyone, stay calm!

558
00:32:39,760 --> 00:32:41,120
Speak one at a time!

559
00:32:41,200 --> 00:32:42,800
Let's talk this through properly.
Everyone, just stay calm.

560
00:32:42,880 --> 00:32:43,880
‪How can I calm down?

561
00:32:47,280 --> 00:32:48,160
Ningsui Police Station.

562
00:32:48,760 --> 00:32:49,600
We received a report

563
00:32:49,680 --> 00:32:51,920
that Hailan Port is involved
in using non-compliant materials,

564
00:32:52,000 --> 00:32:53,320
resulting in casualties.

565
00:32:53,400 --> 00:32:55,400
You'll need to cooperate
with our investigation. Come with us.

566
00:32:55,480 --> 00:32:56,800
No problem.

567
00:32:56,880 --> 00:32:57,880
Chen,

568
00:32:57,960 --> 00:33:00,120
this hasn't been fully investigated yet.
You can't just take him away.

569
00:33:00,920 --> 00:33:03,000
What, you want to come along too?

570
00:33:03,080 --> 00:33:04,000
Kai!

571
00:33:04,840 --> 00:33:07,640
Officer Chen, we did not use
any non-compliant materials.

572
00:33:07,720 --> 00:33:08,760
Could there be some misunderstanding?

573
00:33:08,840 --> 00:33:09,920
I know.

574
00:33:10,000 --> 00:33:12,000
If they really haven't done anything
wrong, nothing will happen to them.

575
00:33:13,320 --> 00:33:14,240
Don't worry.

576
00:33:15,640 --> 00:33:18,240
It's just for the investigation.
I'll go and come back soon.

577
00:33:18,320 --> 00:33:19,960
- You have my word.
- But…

578
00:33:20,040 --> 00:33:22,520
Take care of yourself,
and look after Granny too.

579
00:33:23,240 --> 00:33:24,080
Let's go.

580
00:33:29,040 --> 00:33:31,440
- Mr. Li has been taken away now.
- What do we do now?

581
00:33:31,520 --> 00:33:34,120
Alright, everyone. The police
have now begun an investigation.

582
00:33:34,200 --> 00:33:35,240
Please go home.

583
00:33:35,320 --> 00:33:37,640
Once we have results,
it will be announced to the public.

584
00:33:37,720 --> 00:33:38,720
Please go home.

585
00:33:38,800 --> 00:33:41,080
Well then, we'll wait for your update.

586
00:33:41,160 --> 00:33:43,720
- Yes!
- Right.

587
00:33:43,800 --> 00:33:46,160
- <i>You must give us an explanation!</i>
- <i>You can't just bully us ordinary people!</i>

588
00:33:46,240 --> 00:33:48,080
We are here for justice.

589
00:33:48,160 --> 00:33:50,680
- Someone is standing up for us.
- Right.

590
00:33:50,760 --> 00:33:52,920
- Trust them.
- They're not getting away with this.

591
00:33:53,000 --> 00:33:55,480
- Back to work. Nothing to see here.
- Okay.

592
00:33:55,560 --> 00:33:56,600
Okay, Ms. Ye.

593
00:33:58,600 --> 00:34:01,280
- What about the worker?
- He's fine now. Don't worry.

594
00:34:01,920 --> 00:34:03,120
There's something wrong
with this situation.

595
00:34:03,200 --> 00:34:05,320
There's no way
we used non-compliant materials.

596
00:34:05,400 --> 00:34:06,840
Every construction plan
and architectural design

597
00:34:06,920 --> 00:34:08,400
was reviewed and approved
by every department.

598
00:34:08,920 --> 00:34:10,120
Now that something has happened,

599
00:34:11,080 --> 00:34:12,120
public opinion has completely shifted.

600
00:34:13,679 --> 00:34:15,679
So you're saying someone
is deliberately causing trouble?

601
00:34:16,520 --> 00:34:17,360
That's a possibility.

602
00:34:25,280 --> 00:34:26,560
- Hello.
- <i>Have you seen the news?</i>

603
00:34:26,639 --> 00:34:28,320
<i>Li Lingbai is holding</i>
<i>a press conference tomorrow.</i>

604
00:34:28,400 --> 00:34:29,280
What?

605
00:34:30,960 --> 00:34:32,080
What's wrong?

606
00:34:32,159 --> 00:34:34,840
Li Lingbai is hosting a press conference.
We need to get to the bottom of this

607
00:34:34,920 --> 00:34:36,199
before it takes place.

608
00:34:36,280 --> 00:34:37,960
- Let's head to the site. Go!
- Let's go!

609
00:34:44,320 --> 00:34:46,000
CONSTRUCTION CONTRACT

610
00:34:48,440 --> 00:34:50,239
It doesn't match the material
specifications in the contract.

611
00:34:51,600 --> 00:34:53,719
- Did someone swap the materials?
- Most likely.

612
00:34:54,400 --> 00:34:56,840
When was the last time you were here?

613
00:34:56,920 --> 00:34:58,640
I'll pull the surveillance footage
for this area.

614
00:34:58,720 --> 00:34:59,800
MATERIAL STORAGE AREA

615
00:35:02,320 --> 00:35:04,760
- Zhou Yu!
- Zhou Yu?

616
00:35:05,360 --> 00:35:06,400
Stop!

617
00:35:07,240 --> 00:35:09,440
Stop right there! Don't run, Zhou Yu!

618
00:35:11,880 --> 00:35:12,720
What are you doing here?

619
00:35:13,720 --> 00:35:14,640
I'm telling you.

620
00:35:14,720 --> 00:35:17,240
I'm telling you. I've got evidence
of you swapping materials!

621
00:35:17,920 --> 00:35:19,520
- What evidence?
- What evidence?

622
00:35:19,600 --> 00:35:21,440
Still playing tough, huh? What evidence?

623
00:35:21,520 --> 00:35:23,080
Here, see for yourself.

624
00:35:23,160 --> 00:35:26,040
MATERIAL STORAGE AREA

625
00:35:29,800 --> 00:35:31,240
- This.
- See it clearly now?

626
00:35:32,240 --> 00:35:33,480
You thieves crying "stop thief"!

627
00:35:33,560 --> 00:35:34,560
Thieves crying "stop thief"!

628
00:35:34,640 --> 00:35:36,560
Are there any decent people
in your Hanhai Group?

629
00:35:36,640 --> 00:35:38,840
You're all in cahoots with that
Wang Xingsheng, a bunch of liars

630
00:35:38,920 --> 00:35:40,520
and scoundrels. Get away from me!

631
00:35:40,600 --> 00:35:41,720
Who are you talking about?

632
00:35:42,240 --> 00:35:44,160
Head back first.
I'm going to have a word with him.

633
00:35:45,680 --> 00:35:46,560
Stop!

634
00:35:47,760 --> 00:35:50,000
Mingxiao, I need all the recent
surveillance footage from Hailan Port.

635
00:35:50,080 --> 00:35:50,920
All of it!

636
00:35:52,680 --> 00:35:53,440
Let's go.

637
00:36:12,320 --> 00:36:13,840
- Granny.
- <i>Meng.</i>

638
00:36:13,920 --> 00:36:16,480
Why isn't Badou answering his phone?

639
00:36:16,560 --> 00:36:17,800
Did something happen?

640
00:36:18,680 --> 00:36:19,680
Can't get through?

641
00:36:20,280 --> 00:36:22,480
Probably because he's been working
overtime lately. He's busy.

642
00:36:22,560 --> 00:36:24,080
<i>As long as he's okay.</i>

643
00:36:24,160 --> 00:36:26,560
What's up with this company?

644
00:36:26,640 --> 00:36:29,200
Not even a moment to answer the phone?

645
00:36:29,280 --> 00:36:30,640
Always overtime.

646
00:36:31,160 --> 00:36:32,760
But you two must eat properly.

647
00:36:33,800 --> 00:36:36,000
Don't worry. You get some rest early,

648
00:36:36,080 --> 00:36:37,760
and once we're done here,
we'll come see you, okay?

649
00:36:37,840 --> 00:36:40,120
No need to keep me company.

650
00:36:40,200 --> 00:36:42,400
He should make time
to be with you properly.

651
00:36:42,480 --> 00:36:43,640
You're still newlyweds.

652
00:36:44,280 --> 00:36:46,200
<i>When I see him,</i>
<i>I'll give him a good talking-to.</i>

653
00:36:47,520 --> 00:36:48,800
Alright,

654
00:36:48,880 --> 00:36:50,600
then you get to sleep early.

655
00:36:51,240 --> 00:36:52,440
Alright then, I'm hanging up.

656
00:36:53,120 --> 00:36:54,160
Be good.

657
00:36:59,760 --> 00:37:01,440
How did it go? Did Granny notice anything?

658
00:37:03,320 --> 00:37:06,080
She hasn't noticed yet, but if we drag
this out any longer, she might.

659
00:37:06,880 --> 00:37:08,920
You've been watching for a while now.
Take a break.

660
00:37:09,760 --> 00:37:14,000
I think we should consider other options.
This way isn't making much progress.

661
00:37:28,520 --> 00:37:29,760
Look at this video.

662
00:37:30,520 --> 00:37:33,200
It was taken when I accompanied
Lin Yangyang to the construction site.

663
00:37:33,280 --> 00:37:35,360
The equipment back then was all compliant,

664
00:37:35,440 --> 00:37:36,760
completely different
from what's on the site now.

665
00:37:38,400 --> 00:37:40,520
And look at this here.

666
00:37:42,200 --> 00:37:44,200
This video from that period
has been tampered with.

667
00:37:45,200 --> 00:37:46,120
Exactly.

668
00:37:46,640 --> 00:37:48,600
Now it's up to whether Cheng Kairan
can catch up with Zhou Yu.

669
00:37:51,440 --> 00:37:53,000
- How's it going?
- Did you catch up?

670
00:37:53,080 --> 00:37:54,800
- Yes, I did.
- And then?

671
00:37:55,400 --> 00:37:56,720
This Zhou Yu,

672
00:37:57,600 --> 00:37:59,840
he absolutely refuses
to help Li Jinyu clear his name.

673
00:38:00,440 --> 00:38:02,560
He's hated Hailan Port since he was a kid.

674
00:38:02,640 --> 00:38:04,320
He'd be happy if it went bankrupt.

675
00:38:05,320 --> 00:38:06,560
But without Zhou Yu,

676
00:38:06,640 --> 00:38:08,520
that video footage is useless.

677
00:38:12,360 --> 00:38:14,640
NINGSUI WELFARE CENTER

678
00:38:18,480 --> 00:38:20,360
- Brother Zhou Yu!
- Play here!

679
00:38:20,440 --> 00:38:21,560
Brother Zhou Yu!

680
00:38:22,760 --> 00:38:23,640
Zhou Yu.

681
00:38:23,720 --> 00:38:24,800
Shit!

682
00:38:24,880 --> 00:38:26,760
Don't "shit". Get back here. Come on.

683
00:38:27,760 --> 00:38:29,120
- Stand here.
- Move aside.

684
00:38:30,400 --> 00:38:31,680
Why do you always run?

685
00:38:31,760 --> 00:38:33,240
Run! You never outrun me anyway.

686
00:38:33,320 --> 00:38:34,320
You're going to fall.

687
00:38:35,080 --> 00:38:37,000
What are you here for again?

688
00:38:37,080 --> 00:38:39,040
How many times do I have to say it?

689
00:38:39,120 --> 00:38:40,520
I don't help people get away with crimes.

690
00:38:40,600 --> 00:38:42,720
I've told you just as many times.

691
00:38:42,800 --> 00:38:44,680
The material switching
had nothing to do with Li Jinyu.

692
00:38:44,760 --> 00:38:46,280
It wasn't us.

693
00:38:46,360 --> 00:38:49,680
If you don't speak up, you're basically
helping the bad guys. You get that?

694
00:38:51,600 --> 00:38:52,720
Zhou Yu,

695
00:38:53,320 --> 00:38:55,040
I came here for Li Jinyu,

696
00:38:55,120 --> 00:38:56,600
but I'm not asking you
to lie or give false testimony.

697
00:38:56,680 --> 00:38:59,360
I only hope you can state
the facts as you saw them.

698
00:38:59,440 --> 00:39:02,240
As for the truth, everyone
will draw their own conclusions.

699
00:39:07,640 --> 00:39:08,840
At this welfare center,

700
00:39:09,400 --> 00:39:11,160
all these kids really look up to you.

701
00:39:11,880 --> 00:39:13,520
They see you as a big brother
and role model.

702
00:39:13,600 --> 00:39:15,880
But if you say nothing now,

703
00:39:15,960 --> 00:39:17,880
you could end up protecting a bad person

704
00:39:18,400 --> 00:39:19,720
and framing an innocent one.

705
00:39:21,960 --> 00:39:25,080
That's not the outcome
you want to see, is it?

706
00:39:30,600 --> 00:39:31,720
Think it over again.

707
00:39:32,920 --> 00:39:33,760
The press conference is about to start.

708
00:39:34,840 --> 00:39:37,400
Let's go. Just give it some more thought.

709
00:39:51,080 --> 00:39:52,240
UNSCRUPULOUS BUSINESS

710
00:39:53,280 --> 00:39:57,520
HAILAN PORT PHASE II CONSTRUCTION INCIDENT
PRESS CONFERENCE

711
00:39:57,600 --> 00:39:59,000
HAILAN PORT PROMOTION: BE WITH THE CLOUD
THE VIEW AND THE COOL RIPPLES

712
00:40:00,840 --> 00:40:01,840
Here they are!

713
00:40:01,920 --> 00:40:05,320
- Here they come.
- They come.

714
00:40:05,400 --> 00:40:08,360
Unscrupulous boss, give us an explanation!

715
00:40:08,440 --> 00:40:10,960
Yangyang, I'm embarrassed
you had to see such a serious incident.

716
00:40:11,040 --> 00:40:12,960
Hurry up and give us an explanation!

717
00:40:13,520 --> 00:40:16,280
Later, we'll need you to cooperate with us
in issuing a joint statement.

718
00:40:17,160 --> 00:40:18,040
No problem.

719
00:40:18,120 --> 00:40:20,160
As long as it can help Jinyu.

720
00:40:21,240 --> 00:40:22,200
Mrs. Li.

721
00:40:23,520 --> 00:40:25,240
Yang Bingzhang is already on his way.

722
00:40:26,720 --> 00:40:27,920
How's it going with Wang Xingsheng?

723
00:40:28,000 --> 00:40:30,360
He's keeping quiet. Being watched,
he won't be able to cause any trouble.

724
00:40:30,440 --> 00:40:32,000
You lawless rogue!

725
00:40:35,040 --> 00:40:36,640
Don't leave! You can't go!

726
00:40:36,720 --> 00:40:40,200
HAILAN PORT PHASE II CONSTRUCTION INCIDENT
PRESS CONFERENCE

727
00:40:50,080 --> 00:40:52,960
LI LINGBAI

728
00:40:53,040 --> 00:40:56,520
HAILAN PORT PHASE II CONSTRUCTION INCIDENT
PRESS CONFERENCE

729
00:40:59,680 --> 00:41:01,880
Hello, everyone. I'm Li Lingbai.

730
00:41:02,400 --> 00:41:05,000
Tomorrow is the grand opening
of our Hailan Port.

731
00:41:05,560 --> 00:41:08,320
I never expected to meet you all
under such circumstances today.

732
00:41:08,400 --> 00:41:09,240
LIN YANGYANG

733
00:41:09,320 --> 00:41:11,920
Regarding the collapse incident
at Hailan Port Phase II,

734
00:41:12,800 --> 00:41:14,680
as the chairman of Hanhai Group,

735
00:41:15,200 --> 00:41:16,160
I first want

736
00:41:17,040 --> 00:41:18,960
to offer everyone
my sincere apologies here.

737
00:41:27,200 --> 00:41:30,240
<i>The person responsible for this project</i>
<i>is my eldest son, Li Jinyu.</i>

738
00:41:31,000 --> 00:41:33,680
<i>Hanhai Group will absolutely</i>
<i>take full responsibility,</i>

739
00:41:34,200 --> 00:41:36,720
<i>and I will also deal</i>
<i>with Li Jinyu severely.</i>

740
00:41:37,840 --> 00:41:39,600
The place where Badou works

741
00:41:40,560 --> 00:41:41,880
is Li Lingbai's company.

742
